[06/08/2018 22:00:22] <font color="#00ff00">Pierre Bernard, Bernard,</font>
[06/08/2018 22:00:22] <font color="#00ff00">con "B", de bicarbonato.</font>
[06/08/2018 22:00:23] <font color="#ffffff">Bueno, vamos a ver.</font>
[06/08/2018 22:00:26] <font color="#00ff00">¡Que allí, a ese señor!</font>
[06/08/2018 22:00:26] <font color="#ffffff">¿No vendrá con el equipaje?</font>
