[06/08/2018 22:57:24] <font color="#00ffff">esta fiesta?</font>
[06/08/2018 22:57:26] <font color="#ffffff">A la "mademoiselle".</font>
[06/08/2018 22:57:29] <font color="#ffff00">Sí, he sido yo.</font>
[06/08/2018 22:57:29] <font color="#00ff00">Ivette, eres un sol,</font>
